snippet.title: LET'S PLAY A VISUAL NOVEL: WANrobo - NO COMMENTARY
snippet.description:
Hello, guys!!!!! Welcome back to my channel. Today we'll going to play a NPCKC game: WANrobo, a smart home suite. This game has a well-hitting message, at the begining, it seems that we're trapped in a loop of tasks for 11 days, but in the end, they reveal the heartbroken story of this AI.

Play the game: https://npckc.itch.io/wanrobo
